{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"968903f108","title":"吸引更多胡宗南部于重庆聚牙之","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8455c41410","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":27,"articleId":"968903f108"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"e3622f750b","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"968903f108","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘、邓，指刘伯承、邓小平，当时分别任第二野战军司令员和政治委员。2]贺，指贺龙，当时任西南军区司令员、川西北军政委员会主任。李，指李井泉，当时任川西北军政委员会副主任。"},{"id":"bc70d4f9bf","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"968903f108","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡宗南，当时任国民党军西南军政长官公署副长官。"},{"id":"7d8e35fcf6","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"968903f108","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1949年5月12日至6月2日第三野战军第九、第十兵团举行的上海战役，此役，共歼灭国民党军京沪杭警备总司令汤恩伯所部15万余人。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f8a2ccd41d","type":"title","text":"吸引更多胡宗南部于重庆聚歼之","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"968903f108"},{"id":"e3622f750b","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、邓，并告贺、李P","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"968903f108"},{"id":"bc70d4f9bf","type":"paragraph","text":"据报蒋介石令胡宗南以汽车八百辆运其第三军到重庆。请注意：（一）是否能吸引更多的胡宗南部到重庆。（二）我向重庆方面攻击之各军是否有必要稍为退缓其行为，以利吸引较多之敌军据守重庆而后聚歼之。因为蒋介石自己在重庆，可能打一个聚轩汤恩伯于上海那样的好仗”","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"968903f108"},{"id":"7d8e35fcf6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"968903f108"},{"id":"908629f5ea","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月二十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"968903f108"}],"page":{"id":"7364cfb94d","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articl